A Lagos State resident and Master of Ceremony, simply identified as Emmanuel Chigozie, has allegedly beat his pregnant wife to death, at their residence in Okota area of the state.It was learnt that the couple got married four years ago, after Chigozie was alleged to have repeatedly cheated and subjected his wife to domestic abuse after she had their first child.The MC is also accused of assaulting his pregnant wife who was rushed to the hospital but died alongside her baby after she demanded for the N2.7million she loaned him.Itunu was said to have had fears since December 2021 of having complications during childbirth due to continuous physical abuse she had allegedly been subjected to by her husband.